SUMMARY:Closure: BARONS COURT STATION: From Monday 19 January to Sunday 7 
 June\, eastbound trains will not call at Barons Court. If travelling 
 eastbound from the station\, please use westbound District or Piccadilly 
 line trains and change to eastbound services at Hammersmith. If travelling
  eastbound to the station\, please continue to West Kensington (on the 
 District line) or Earls Court (on the Piccadilly line) and change to 
 westbound services.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260308T053142Z
UID:160e67bd-1ab0-11f1-bc25-7c1e52accbd4
DTSTART:20260307
DTEND:20260309
SUMMARY:Part Closure: PICCADILLY LINE: Saturday 7 and Sunday 8 March 
 (Including Friday and Saturday Night Tube)\, no service between 
 Cockfosters and Uxbridge. Trains continue to operate between Acton Town 
 and Heathrow. Use METROPOLITAN LINE trains between Rayners Lane and 
 Uxbridge and ELIZABETH LINE services between Central London and Heathrow. 
 Replacement buses operate.
END:VEVENT
